To fetch data from navigationProperties or associated entities using the SmartTable control in SAPUI5, you can bind the SmartTable to a specific entity set that includes the navigation properties or associated entities. Below is an example code snippet to demonstrate this:

```javascript
// Assuming you have a SmartTable control defined in your view
var oSmartTable = new sap.ui.comp.smarttable.SmartTable({
    entitySet: "YourEntitySet", // Main entity set that includes the navigation properties
