        <input {...register("lastName", { required: true })} />
        {errors.lastName && <span>This field is required</span>}
      </div>
      <button type="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
  );
}
```

Please note that `handleSubmit` will also trigger validation and call the `onSubmit` function only if the form inputs are valid. So if you submit the form without touching any inputs, it will skip validation and directly call the `onSubmit` function.

